{"tid":2129951,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人既同事好寸？","createTime":"2020-07-29T03:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T07:24:25.000Z","uid":354503,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb0c68fae4a2445f2eb35473355c80616db553e","tid":2129951,"uid":354503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，我話自己行路會喘氣又話我咁既身形梗係喘啦<br />\n又話我唔靚<br />\n好啦，尋日又話我大學正啦，可以收兵請人做功課<br />\n<br />\n我自問無得罪過佢囉<br />\n又無同佢做過野<br />\n又無同佢傾過計<br />\n平日都無乜交雜<br />\n又唔係同佢食lunch<br />\n<br />\n憑咩啊？又唔係我老細<br />\n番工又要俾佢寸，好好玩？<br />\n係咪以為你自己好巴閉好勁啊？<br />\n男人喎，成個女人咁款單單打打<br />\n最弊係我無寸過佢無同佢溝通過<br />\n我得罪佢啲乜啊屌<br />\n係咪我存在已經係罪過<br />\n屌<br />\n你乜水啊 係咪以為係我老細？你係cheap雞同事咋"},{"pid":"c832b90d24690286dee4bc977ce015c045c45fa4","tid":2129951,"uid":362900,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"當面屌啦<br />\n上黎放屁有7用咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52160f6cd6d1ad9b329787d99971bea83aa55970","tid":2129951,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"直接屌鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"654f1d2d7f42c2f6f6576e6e23ee9d3882468dae","tid":2129951,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"寸你就梗架啦"},{"pid":"ede60e05c481c72e8afb290a1ad66840b73cbff2","tid":2129951,"uid":354503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c832b90d24690286dee4bc977ce015c045c45fa4","tid":2129951,"uid":362900,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"當面屌啦<br />\n上黎放屁有7用咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"尋日聽完呆左，反應唔切"},{"pid":"26ee9d03a5757722daf76fa6ecdb03642b199ce3","tid":2129951,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ede60e05c481c72e8afb290a1ad66840b73cbff2","tid":2129951,"uid":354503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83